{"parse": {"title": "Colver", "pageid": 34336, "text": {"*": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><div class=\"eraicon filtericon\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpunk_2077\" title=\"Cyberpunk 2077\"><img alt=\"2077Icon\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/7/77/2077Icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/80?cb=20180612180205\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"20\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"2077Icon.png\" data-image-key=\"2077Icon.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Phantom_Liberty\" title=\"Phantom Liberty\"><img alt=\"Logo CP2077PL\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/b/ba/Logo_CP2077PL.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/80?cb=20231020113357\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"9\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Logo CP2077PL.png\" data-image-key=\"Logo_CP2077PL.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" /></a></span></div>\n<p>\n<aside role=\"region\" class=\"portable-infobox pi-background pi-border-color pi-theme-wikia pi-layout-default\">\n<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-item-spacing pi-title pi-secondary-background\" data-source=\"title\">Colver</h2>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Biographical Information</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"status\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Status</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Alive</div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Physical Information</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"gender\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Gender</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Male</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"hair_color\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Hair Color</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Black</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"eyes\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Eye Color</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Blue</div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Faction Information</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"occupation\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Occupation</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Reverend<br />Televangelist<br />President of the Church of Eliyahu the Last Emancipator</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"role\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Role</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Media\" title=\"Media\">Media</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Other Information</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"voiced_by\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Voiced By</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"https://www.imdb.com/find?q=nm0195702\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"imdb:nm0195702\">Michael Gregory</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color pi-collapse pi-collapse-closed\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Appearances</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"appears_games\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Game(s)</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><i><a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpunk_2077\" title=\"Cyberpunk 2077\">Cyberpunk 2077</a></i></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n<b>Colver</b> is a <a href=\"/wiki/Media\" title=\"Media\">Media</a> in <i><a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpunk_2077\" title=\"Cyberpunk 2077\">Cyberpunk 2077</a></i>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fcyberpunk.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FColver%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"divTable bannercurve\"><i>This section requires expanding. <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"text\" href=\"https://cyberpunk.fandom.com/wiki/Colver?action=edit\">Click here to add more.</a></i><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"text\" href=\"https://cyberpunk.fandom.com/wiki/Colver?action=edit\">\ud83d\udcdd</a></div>\n<p>Colver wears all black futuristic clerical clothing of a Catholic priest, including a collar. He also has a golden crucifix <a href=\"/wiki/Cyberware\" title=\"Cyberware\">implanted</a> on his forehead.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Biography\">Biography</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fcyberpunk.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FColver%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"divTable bannercurve\"><i>This section requires expanding. <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"text\" href=\"https://cyberpunk.fandom.com/wiki/Colver?action=edit\">Click here to add more.</a></i><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"text\" href=\"https://cyberpunk.fandom.com/wiki/Colver?action=edit\">\ud83d\udcdd</a></div>\n<p>Colver is the president of a mega church known as the Church of Eliyahu the Last Emancipator. He appears on <a href=\"/wiki/Night_After_Night_with_Ziggy_Q\" title=\"Night After Night with Ziggy Q\">Night After Night with Ziggy Q</a> debating <a href=\"/wiki/Karina_Lee\" title=\"Karina Lee\">Karina Lee</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Chip_In_(TV_show)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Chip In (TV show)\">Chip In</a> debating the moral and ethics of the <a href=\"/wiki/Arasaka\" title=\"Arasaka\">Arasaka</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Relic\" title=\"Relic\">Relic</a> chip. The Reverend, who <a href=\"/wiki/Ziggy_Q\" title=\"Ziggy Q\">Ziggy Q</a> names the bane of Arasaka's PR department, objects to Karina's excitement about the chip. Colver cites that it is a golden calf and an empty promise of immortality that only the rich will be able to afford. He ends his rebuke by explaining that those \"preserved\" within the Relic are algorithms impersonating lost loved ones. Ziggy attempts to provoke Colver by comparing the services of the Relic to a church. The interview end with the reverend questioning if the increased availability of <a href=\"/wiki/Cyberware\" title=\"Cyberware\">cyberware</a> has made humanity happy and how the Relic will lead to eternal suffering where people are haunted by the voices of the dead.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>1<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/wiki/V\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"V\">V</a> can encounter Colver at the bar during <a href=\"/wiki/Kurt_Hansen\" title=\"Kurt Hansen\">Kurt Hansen</a>'s part at the <a href=\"/wiki/Black_Sapphire\" title=\"Black Sapphire\">Black Sapphire</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/Solomon_Reed\" title=\"Solomon Reed\">Solomon Reed</a> raises the question to V over whether he is there to receive a donation for his church or save the soul of Hansen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Quest1_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Quest1-2\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>2<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fcyberpunk.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FColver%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"width:auto; min-height:6em; max-height:12em; height:auto; background-color:;; overflow:auto; margin-bottom:3px; padding: 0.2em 0.5em 0em 0.5em; border:1px solid var(--cyberpunkwiki-accent-color);\">\n<div class=\"references-small\"><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">\u2191</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/mi9fh0-GpNw\">Night After Night with Ziggy Q - Arasaka Relic Chip Debate</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Quest1-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Quest1_2-0\">\u2191</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/wiki/You_Know_My_Name\" title=\"You Know My Name\">You Know My Name</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div></div>\n</div>"}, "images": ["2077Icon.png", "Logo_CP2077PL.png"]}}